title: Vin Diesel plays Dungeons and Dragons, unleashes his inner nerd
text:
Vin Diesel plays Dungeons and Dragons, unleashes his inner nerd 
Published By: Mashable - Today 
Actor and karaoke star Vin Diesel sat down with Nerdist for a dramatic round of one of his all-time favorite games: Dungeons and Dragons.
